snippet.title: GR8IMAGES
snippet.description: Hi I'm a real life celebrity/paparazzi event and candid photographer based in New York.  I've created this channel to share to the world the what's it like to be living and working as a celebrity photographer in New York.  My videos are raw and straight from the red carpet, or the street.   Subscribe for the newest and exclusive content from NYC!
